com.cyc.kb

Interface Fact

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Assertion, KbObject, KbObject.KbObjectWithArity
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FactWrapper

    public interface Fact
extends Assertion
    The interface for Assertions that relate KbCollections and KbIndividuals to each other and to primitive values such as numbers and strings. The vast majority of Assertions are of this type.
